e United States, derailing television broadcasts in Britain and impacting telecommunications in Australia.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997723741392874, \"rank\": 0.0002276775970368784, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 805, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999982521398393, \"rank\": 1.487803451856534e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999464203963553, \"rank\": 5.306816991128301e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris 2024 is aware of global technical issues affecting Microsoft software.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"score\": 0.9998538405512586, \"rank\": 0.00014112439277130592, \"text\": \"Microsoft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Microsoft\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These issues are impacting Paris 2024's IT operations,\\\" organisers said.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris 2024's technical teams have been fully mobilised to mitigate the impacts of these issues and we have activated contingency plans in order to continue operations,\\\" they added.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\